                    is back ordered and not be available to ship.
            </p>

            <h4>Credit Cards</h4>

            <p>
                Credit card charges are submitted at the time when payment information is verified.
                    Only if the item is a computer parts, backordered and not a customer requested special
                    order, the credit card charge will be submitted at the time of shipping.
            </p>
            <p>
                Merchandise will be shipped to your credit card billing address which is displayed
