            </h4>

            <p>
                PayPal payment is accepted for an order to be shipped to a PayPal Confirmed Address
                    only; PayPal will not be accepted for any pickup orders. Any PayPal payment with
                    an unconfirmed address will be refused.
            </p>

            <h4>Check Payment
            </h4>

            <p>
                LU Computers will accept a cashiers check or money order on all orders shipped by
                    Carrier. LU Computers will accept personal and business checks for prepay orders,
                    but allow 10-24 business days for clearing.
            </p>

