                fraud, and immediately report it to the FBI and higher authorities. All deliveries
                REQUIRE A SIGNATURE to be released. Recipient must be at the shipping address during
                the day to sign and accept the package. If no one is present to accept the package,
                please contact the carrier to arrange the delivery.
            </p>
